{"tid":451665,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲首富李嘉誠為什麼偏愛這款LG手機?","createTime":"2017-10-29T12:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T11:34:56.000Z","uid":47132,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"edbb6778f36aba0f61b14d89c20c21196b9f6ed3","tid":451665,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ifun01.com/images/2017/01/17/05/1303_33PSbA_94R4f8.jpg!r550x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ifun01.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F05%2F1303_33PSbA_94R4f8.jpg%21r550x0.jpg&h=5ed18f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機已經是全人類生活中必備的東西之一了，更有一句話證明了手機的重要性，手機是自古以來第一個可以讓人攜帶24小時的產物。而亞洲首富李嘉誠這樣的人物，會用什麼手機呢？ 下面這部手機，如果光看他的造型，第一反應就是它是屬于上個世紀的產物。按照時間上來說，確實已經屬于&ldquo;古董&rdquo;層級的產物，不過這樣一款古董層級的手機，它主人卻是亞洲首富。<br />\n<br />\n這部LG手機的主人就是李嘉誠，身為亞洲的首富，李嘉誠在生活上似乎沒有任何奢華享受的習慣，包括他使用的手機。這部手機的型號是U8210，是當年LG公司少量生產贈送給社會名流的手機，手機鍍有黃金，是一部很有紀念意義的手機，李嘉誠一直使用了好久，並沒有刻意跟隨智能手機的潮流，而是用蘋果手機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=179a6t9/1qp300006p269p185rr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D179a6t9%2F1qp300006p269p185rr6.jpg&h=cef0291d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77cbf407c1310b672b7b158854bcc3ad723634c1","tid":451665,"uid":192,"like":15,"dislike":62,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"佢咁有錢<br />\n用咩都好啦-.-"},{"pid":"da733aa96acc218528dfdd40f5286d6c2dd3e61c","tid":451665,"uid":4502,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:33:23.000Z","msg":"當年第一步3G手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屋企都有部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0291baa49cf654953e39093f0d7ca9d38aa3f73d","tid":451665,"uid":4502,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年第一部3G手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/t